# Content-hashed cache trees are served from the persistent R2 bucket
# (assets.jiki.io) via assetsUrl(), never from the worker's bundled static assets
# (which are destroyed on every redeploy, breaking in-flight sessions). Keep them
# out of the worker bundle — they're uploaded to R2 immutably by `static:upload`.
static/i18n/*
static/exercises/*
static/concepts/*
static/content/*
static/hashed/*
